<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>飞行器动力工程（航天工程）拟人化</p><br><p>我以为：</p><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/aaf034bab88d9b2f0d43f51ff56c7ad2_b.jpg" data-rawheight="404" data-rawwidth="611" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="611" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/aaf034bab88d9b2f0d43f51ff56c7ad2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="404" data-rawwidth="611" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="611" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/aaf034bab88d9b2f0d43f51ff56c7ad2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/aaf034bab88d9b2f0d43f51ff56c7ad2_b.jpg"><br><p>实际上：</p><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/97f4bea68e9fe982f39ce367a225ffd3_b.jpg" data-rawheight="429" data-rawwidth="302" class="content_image" width="302"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="429" data-rawwidth="302" class="content_image lazy" width="302" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/97f4bea68e9fe982f39ce367a225ffd3_b.jpg"><br><br><p>娘化太难了，弄出来叫啥，箭娘？</p>


